<SECOND>BC-Quotes,0182</SECOND>
<HEAD>Current Quotations</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 `` What I have seen is total devastation. I've never seen snakes as big as I've seen in the past few days, every time we pick up a board.'' _ Police Officer <PERSON> Tom </PERSON> <PERSON> Buchanan </PERSON>, after surveying damage wrought in Isle of Palms, <LOCATION> S.C. </LOCATION>, by Hurricane Hugo.
