 breeding areas when the old ones were about to be disturbed by a dam under construction in <LOCATION> Chile </LOCATION>. Other projects will help manage forests in <LOCATION> Sri </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Lanka </LOCATION> and promote reforestation in <LOCATION> Bangladesh </LOCATION>.
