<HEAD>GAO Faults FAA on Enforcing New Airline Security Measures</HEAD>
<HEAD>With Flight 103,Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By DIANE DUSTON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
