<SECOND>BC-History, Adv01,0551</SECOND>
<HEAD>$adv01</HEAD>
<HEAD>For Release Sunday, Oct. 1</HEAD>
<HEAD>Today In History</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
