ON>,'' <PERSON> Hrab </PERSON> said. <PERSON> Hrab </PERSON> said he will continue to oversee operations at Cominso's plant, which employs about 30 people in <LOCATION> Montreal </LOCATION> `` We figure we will double our employees because we expect Celestial to have a very big push in <LOCATION> Canada </LOCATION>,'' he said. Once bought by <PERSON> Kraft </PERSON>, <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION>, Celestial regained its independence Nov. 2 when a management and investor group bought it back.
